title: Express Scripts CEO George Paz Plans to Retire
text:
Express Scripts Holding Co. said longtime Chairman and Chief Executive George Paz plans to retire from the helm of the pharmacy-benefits manager and named company President Tim Wentworth as his successor.
Mr. Paz plans to retire next year after the companyâ€™s annual shareholder meeting, which is set for May. He will stay on as nonexecutive chairman and Thomas Mac Mahon will continue as lead independent director.
